Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time elapsed from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' until 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Minimum time between 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time for a manuscript to reach 'SW-Reviewer Declined' status after 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' in the review process
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Reviewer Declined and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'SW-Reviewer Declined' from 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Total time it takes 'SW-Reviewer Declined' after the execution of 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time it takes the 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to be followed by 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time to 'SW-Reviewer Declined' since the 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: 'SW-Reviewer Declined' Cycle Time in comparison to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Reviewer Selection is 3 days late'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is 3 days late'

Name: Total time for 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to lead to a 'SW-EIC Major Revision' decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Reviewer Declined' before reaching 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time for 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to impact the subsequent 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' cycle
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Reviewer Declined' to 'SW-Reviewer No Response' occurrence
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'
